  "page": "Smiling Sea",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Summer Isles and the location of the Smiling Sea\"><img alt=\"The Summer Isles and the location of the Smiling Sea\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg/300px-Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg/450px-Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/54/Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg/600px-Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 45%; left: 49.4%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"The Summer Isles and the location of the Smiling Sea\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Smiling Sea\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; top:-2.65em; left:-3em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Smiling Sea</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a> and the location of the Smiling Sea\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Smiling Sea</b> is a body of water in the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>. It separates the islands of <a href=\"/index.php/Walano\" title=\"Walano\">Walano</a>, to the north, from <a href=\"/index.php/Omboru\" title=\"Omboru\">Omboru</a>, to the south and east. In its center is the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Birds\" title=\"Isle of Birds\">Isle of Birds</a>, that is south of <a href=\"/index.php/Tall_Trees_Town\" title=\"Tall Trees Town\">Tall Trees Town</a>. The island of <a href=\"/index.php/Koj\" title=\"Koj\">Koj</a> separates it from the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Sea\" title=\"Summer Sea\">Summer Sea</a> on the west.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafsmiling_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafsmiling_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smiling_Sea&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafsmiling_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafsmiling_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Smiling Sea.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The West.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Summer_Isles\" title=\"Template:Summer Isles\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Summer_Isles&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Summer Isles (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Summer_Isles&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">The Summer Isles</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Islands</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bones\" title=\"Bones\">The Bones</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Doquu\" title=\"Doquu\">Doquu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Birds\" title=\"Isle of Birds\">Isle of Birds</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Love\" titl